text: Bus 160 is shitty and infrequent. One bus serving the entire route at 9pm? Shame on you.
Spacious but stop, cross over via the bridge.

It is along Woodlands Road, just opposite the Kranji Mrt Station.There is an overhead link way linking both of them.Here and the opposite bus stop at the Kranji Mrt Stn have buses going to Johor Baru.On week ends can see queues of passengers, more so on long week end holidays, sometimes the queue is quite long.

Dated : 11/12/2018 ( Tuesday ).
